OL,6,FThe family of a knife crime victim
OL,7,Ffrom Gloucester is calling for changes
OL,8,Fin law after the election to protect
OL,9,Fother tragedies from happening.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country, the
OL,12,Fgrandmother of Ramarni Crosby, who was
OL,13,Fstabbed to death in 2021, says stop
OL,14,Fand search powers for the police
OL,15,Fshould be improved.
OL,17,FRamarni's grandmother, Viv Clifford,
OL,18,Fsaid: "There are no powers to stop and
OL,19,Fsearch these kids. So they're walking
OL,20,Faround knowing that they're not going
OL,21,Fto get searched.
